      <div style="background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,53,.15);border-radius:14px;padding:1.3rem"><div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:.4rem">🍭</div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:.3rem"> Vată de Zahăr (2 ore)</div><div style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem">280 RON</div><div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.6">Mașina profesională + operator + zahăr colorat nelimitat. 200+ porții posibile. Culorile la alegere</div></div><div style="background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,53,.15);border-radius:14px;padding:1.3rem"><div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:.4rem">🍿</div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:.3rem"> Popcorn (2 ore)</div><div style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem">250 RON</div><div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.6">Aparat popcorn profesional + operator + porumb și unt nelimitat. Variante: sarat, dulce, caramel</div></div><div style="background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,53,.15);border-radius:14px;padding:1.3rem"><div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:.4rem">🎪</div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:.3rem"> Combo Vată + Popcorn (2 ore)</div><div style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem">450 RON</div><div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.6">Ambele mașini + operator pentru fiecare. Stația dublă care face senzație la orice petrecere mare</div></div><div style="background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,53,.15);border-radius:14px;padding:1.3rem"><div style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:.4rem">⏰</div><div style="font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:.3rem">Extensie orar (1h)</div><div style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem">120 RON</div><div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.6">Adaugă o oră extra la orice pachet. Recomandat pentru petreceri cu 40+ invitați sau programe lungi</div></div>
